tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE QuantumCircuits (
  circuit_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  circuit_name VARCHAR(50),
  circuit_description TEXT,
  algorithm_id INT,
  FOREIGN KEY (algorithm_id) REFERENCES QuantumAlgorithms(algorithm_id)
);

CREATE TABLE gates (
  gate_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  gate_name TEXT NOT NULL,
  gate_type TEXT NOT NULL,
  circuit_id UUID NOT NULL,
  FOREIGN KEY (circuit_id) REFERENCES quantum_circuits(circuit_id)
);
